---
title: Citrus Skillet Shrimp over Basmati Rice
description: Succulent shrimp, sweet poblano pepper, and tangy olives are finished with a burst of citrus in this quick skillet sauté. The sauce uses a combo of orange and lemon juices and zests to keep things bright and sunshine-y. Plain basmati rice is all that’s needed to accompany it on the plate—the grains do a great job of soaking up all those vibrant flavors.
